title: Example of OCE Teams
body:
I called mid in norms, and didn't watch the chat until we were all locked in and realised that mid was already called, so I went Katarina support and carried the team, they then decided to surrender because I was an "A-Hole" the only thing I said in the whole game was "mid" in pre game lobby, the whole game I didn't talk at all. We could've won that game too.
A-Hole Kalista.... rich kid..
